/*
Quality Settings Reference:
- 144p (256×144) - Very slow connections
- 240p (426×240) - Slow connections  
- 360p (640×360) - Basic streaming
- 480p (854×480) - Standard definition
- 720p (1280×720) - High definition (recommended)
- 1080p (1920×1080) - Full HD (default)
- 1440p (2560×1440) - 2K resolution
- 2160p (3840×2160) - 4K resolution
- 4k (3840×2160) - 4K resolution (alias)

Recommended maxQuality values:
- Smooth playback: 720p or 1080p
- Slow connections: 480p or 360p
- High-end systems: 1080p or 1440p
- Avoid: 2160p/4k (may cause stuttering)
